### LOOP

```
car = {
    "brand" : "BMW" ,
    "model" : "GT" ,
    "year" : 1988
}
# 값을 하나씩 인쇄 
for x in car:
  print(car[x])
```

```
car = {
    "brand" : "BMW" ,
    "model" : "GT" ,
    "year" : 1988
}
for x in car.values():
  print(x)
```

```
car = {
    "brand" : "BMW" ,
    "model" : "GT" ,
    "year" : 1988
}
for x,y in car.items():
  print(x,y)
```

